{"rightSidebarLinks":[{"id":"multilingual validation messages","title":"Multilingual Validation Messages","subLink":null},{"id":"rootmoduleconfiguration","title":"Root Module Configuration","subLink":[]},{"id":"example","title":"Example","subLink":[]}],"title":"Multilingual Validation Messages","description":"","validatorType":"validators","validationTypeTitle":"Validators","type":"tabs","gitDocPath":"https://github.com/rxweb/rxweb.io/edit/master/docs/angular/reactive-forms/how-to/multilingualValidationMessage.md","category":"how-to","subCategory":"","linkTitle":"multilingualValidationMessage","tabArray":{"complete":[{"tabName":"Example","tabGroupContent":null,"content":"<div component=\"app-example-runner\" ref-component=\"app-multilingualValidationMessage-complete\"></div>\r\n"},{"tabName":"Component","tabGroupContent":null,"content":"<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"multilingualValidationMessage-complete-component\"></div> \r\n"},{"tabName":"Html","tabGroupContent":null,"content":"<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"multilingualValidationMessage-complete-html\"></div> \r\n"}]},"innerHtml":null,"htmlContent":"<p class='showHideElement' >For using the multililingual validation messages in angular reactive forms while using <span class='highlighted'>@rxweb/reactive-form-validators</span>, This is done by setting the configuration of <span class='highlighted'>ReactiveFormConfig</span> in the root component, the <span class='highlighted'>errorMessage</span> property in the component html will bind the validation message according to the selected language. For multilingual validation message setup. Please refer <a class=\"redirect-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://docs.rxweb.io/ngx-translate-extension/validation-message\">Validation Message Using ngx-translate-extension</a> </p>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'rootmoduleconfiguration'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Root Module Configuration<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/how-to/multilingualValidationMessage/validators#rootmoduleconfiguration'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<div component=\"app-code\" key=\"multilingualValidationMessage-complete-config\"></div>\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >Lets see how multilingual validation message is achieved using reactive form validators</p>\r\n</div></div>\r\n<div class='row page-section' id= 'example'>\r\n<div class='col-lg-12'>\r\n<h2>Example<a title='Link to this heading' class='link-header' href='/how-to/multilingualValidationMessage/validators#example'><i class='fa fa-link'></i></a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p class='showHideElement' >In the below example, the firstName has the required validator applied and the userName field has alpha validator applied. The validation messages are resolved from the <span class='highlighted'>i18n</span> folder of the assets and bind using the errorMessage property.</p>\r\n<div component=\"app-tabs\" key=\"complete\"></div>\r\n</div></div>\r\n"}